<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Kalgold in talks, cautions shareholders.</title>
<headline>Kalgold in talks, cautions shareholders.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-02-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Kalahari Goldridge Mining Co Ltd said on Wednesday it was in talks which could affect its share price.</p>
<p>It advised shareholders to exercise caution in their share dealings until further notice.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482-1003</p>
